e: ￹`Ta'elifen~ `no~ `paliding~ `kako~.￺A vehicle passed me.￻車子越過了我
￹`Ira~ `ko~ `Pi~`ta'elif~`an~ `a~ `Lisin~ `no~ `Yotaya~ `a~ `tamdaw~.￺The Jews have a Passover feast.￻猶太人有逾越節
￹`Ma~`ta'elif~ `to~ `kita~ `i~ `lalan~.￺We passed each other on the road.￻我們在路上互相交錯
d.f: ￹￺to pass by * to go on beyond￻越過，超過
